high_descs: Move to the center island.
Pick up the bowl next to the lettuce.
Bring the bowl to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Bring the bowl to the counter right of the sink.
Put the bowl in the cabinet to the right below the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in a lower cabinet.

high_descs: Head forward towards the counter and face left in front of the lettuce.
Pick up square bowl from the counter.
Turn right, then right again to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the square bowl inside, close it, then take it out again.
Turn left to see the lower brown cabinet.
Open the lower brown cabinet, put the square bowl inside and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a square bowl away in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn slightly right, then left and walk to the island, then turn left to face the island.
Pick up the tub off of the counter
Turn around and face the fridge
Open the fridge, put the tub in there and then close the door. Wait a few seconds and then retrieve the tub and close the door again.
Turn to your left
Open the kitchen cabinet and place the tub in it, before closing the door
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plastic tub in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Cross the room and turn left at the fridge to face the brown counter.
Pick up the clear, square container to the left of the lettuce on the counter top.
Turn around to face the black fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the clear container on the second shelf in the middle, close the door to let the container chill for a moment, open the door, pick up the clear container and close the door.
Turn to your left to face the lower brown cabinets.
Open the tall cabinet on the far lower right side, put the clear container inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled container in a tall cabinet.
